<h1>36. Indirect Tax Risk and Opportunity Mapping Engine</h1>
<h2 id="description">1. Description</h2>
<p>This diagnostic evaluates exposure to indirect taxes (VAT, GST, sales/use tax) across business units and geographies, identifies compliance risks, and pinpoints refund opportunities or rate misapplications.</p>
<h2 id="when-to-use">2. When to Use</h2>
<p>Ideal during compliance reviews, ERP transitions, or global expansions. Clients benefit by reducing audit exposure, recovering overpaid tax, and automating tax compliance processes.</p>
<p>3. Steps</p>
<p>Review transaction-level tax data and tax codes</p>
<p>Identify mismatches between business activity and tax treatment</p>
<p>Analyze exemption certificate coverage</p>
<p>Benchmark effective rates by geography/product</p>
<p>Recommend process automation, recovery actions, or advisory paths</p>
<p>4. Data Sources</p>
<p>AP and AR transaction data</p>
<p>Tax determination logic in ERP</p>
<p>Exemption certificates</p>
<p>Tax rate tables and jurisdiction rules</p>
<p>Historical audits and assessments</p>
